Roadmap:

Version 0.80:
-------------

- support story file version 5
- TODO

Version 0.75:
-------------

- support story file version 4
- support font styles, toggable buffering
- extend object table
- support timed input
- translate packed addresses differently
- opcodes:
  - new:                  - changed:                 - illegal:
    1. call_2s              1. save                    show_status
    2. call_1s              2. restore
    3. call_vs2             3. call (-> call_vs)
    4. erase_window         4. sread
    5. erase_line
    6. set_cursor
    7. get_cursor
    8. set_text_style
    9. buffer_mode
    10. read_char
    11. scan_table        
    
Version 0.70
-------------

- support story file version 3
- provide Swing application and applet interfaces
- support streams and screen model 3
- support ZSCII and encoded ZSCII
- support Quetzal save game format

